snippet.title: Cosmic Kites | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
For frequent updates regarding Cosmic Kites, follow us on Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/FishmooseInteractive/

Cosmic Kites is a modern and more energetic take on “Snake” but with dragons, lasers and explosions. The game features both a single player and a local multiplayer mode for up to four players.

Steam Greenlight-page: 
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=600340954

Trailer by Pontus Johansson
